regarding your advertisement:\n\n`[AD.NAME]`.\n\nUser [FROM.NAME], have a message for you:\n\n[DESCRIPTION]\n\n[URL.QL]\n\nRegards!','arivu.sacs@gmail.com','2016-02-11 22:41:17','email',1),(198,'en_US',0,'New review for [AD.TITLE] [RATE]','ad-review','[URL.QL]\n\n[RATE]\n\n[DESCRIPTION]','arivu.sacs@gmail.com','2016-02-11 22:41:17','email',1),(199,'en_US',0,'About Us','about-us','<p>The way we advertise or discover what we want as people has evolved over the years, we have gradually moved away from the old methods of advertising on the back pages of physical newspapers/magazines, radio and television onto the use of digital platforms as we are now officially in the Internet age, where nearly all business transactions are conducted online. This has resulted in the emergence of numerous poorly managed classified ads websites that can barely provide their users with the great experience they desire.</p><p>Established in 2016, by Ernest Osaseri a web security specialist / entrepreneur, Plannetads.com is a website (\"The Site\") that hosts classified advertising and related content created and developed by third-party users within the UK. This site offers a free, high quality, reliable and efficient advertisement platform to all users with the outmost confidentiality and customer service.</p><p>Our vision is to facilitate smooth dealings between our users as we remain focused on our mission to create a safe atmosphere and a better market place for everyone. And not forgetting to mention our ultimate aim of providing a fair, responsive, secure and user friendly platform for both sellers and buyers alike. We sort to maintain a lasting relationship with you and gain your trust by creating successful trade connections between individuals just like you as people of one community. All of the above is what makes us (<a href=\"index.html\">Plannetads.com</a>) \"The Site\" to go to when it comes to classified ads.</p>',NULL,'2016-02-15 12:05:58','page',1),(200,'en_US',0,'Privacy Policy','privacy-policy','<p>plannetads.com respect your privacy. Here is our Privacy Policy for this Site:</p><h4 class=\"uk-text-bold\">Acceptance of Privacy Policy</h4> <p>Each time you access, use, post, submit a post or reply, or browse the Site, you signify your acceptance of the then-current Privacy Policy. If you do not accept this Privacy Policy, you are not authorized to use the Site and must discontinue use of the Site immediately.</p><h4 class=\"uk-text-bold\"> Collection and Use of Personal Information </h4> <p> We collect personal information about you whenever you engage in commerce transactions on the Site, use the Site’s products or services, request information or materials, create or update account information, place orders or make purchases, communicate with us, or visit the Site. The personal information we collect and store about you may include without limitation your first and last name, email address, credit or debit card number, telephone numbers, billing and other non-public information about you. </p><p>We may use the information we collect to:</p><ul> <li>Provide superior services;</li><li>Keep you apprised of information and developments that you may find of interest;</li><li>Alert you to new features, terms, content, products or services;</li><li>Contact you regarding your posts, replies, and/or account information;</li><li>Process and respond to your inquires;</li></ul> <h4 class=\"uk-text-bold\"> Disclosure of Personal Information to Third Parties </h4> <p> We may disclose your personal information to agents and operators under confidentiality or similar agreements, including shippers, vendors, payment processors, and advertisers, who we believe reasonably need to come into contact with that information: (i) to provide products or services to you; (ii) to administer our business or the Site, including fulfilling and shipping orders; (iii) to provide customer service; (iv) to update account information; (v) to forward updates, announcements, and newsletters; (vi) to respond to your communications, and communicate with you about the Site and other activities related to the Site; (vii) in the event of any reorganization, merger, sale, joint venture, assignment, transfer or disposition of all or any portion of the Site’s business or operations (including without limitation in connection with bankruptcy or any similar proceedings); or (viii) as otherwise authorized by you. </p>',NULL,'2016-02-15 15:16:48','page',1),(201,'en_US',0,'Terms of Service','terms-of-service','<h4 class=\"uk-text-bold\">Objectives:</h4> <p>Plannetads.com is a web site (the \"Site\") that hosts classified advertising and related content created and developed by third-party users. Your use of the Site, including all access, services and/or features, is governed by these Terms of Use and the Privacy Policy (collectively, \"Terms\"), and you should review both carefully. By using the Site in any way, you are agreeing to comply with these Terms.</p><p> The Site reserves the right to change the Terms at any time and for any reason. Updated versions of the Terms will be posted to the Site at plannetads.com and you should visit this page periodically to keep apprised of any changes. By continuing to use the Site after any such change, you accept and agree to the modified Terms. The Site reserves the right to modify or discontinue, temporarily or permanently, the Site, any site features, benefits (including without limitation blocking or terminating your Account), rules or conditions, all without notice, even though such changes may affect the way you use the Site. You agree that the Site will not be liable to you or any third-party for any modification or discontinuance of the Site. </p><h4 class=\"uk-text-bold\">User Conduct:</h4> <p>Without limitation, you agree to refrain from the following actions while using the Site:</p><ol> <li> <p> Harassing, threatening, embarrassing or causing distress or discomfort upon another individual or entity or impersonating any other person or entity or otherwise restricting or inhibiting any other person from using or enjoying the Site;</p></li><li> <p>Transmitting any information, data, text, files, links, software, chats, communication or other materials that is unlawful, false, misleading, harmful, threatening, abusive, invasive of another\'s privacy, harassing, defamatory, vulgar, obscene, hateful or racially or otherwise objectionable, including without limitation material of any kind or nature that encourages conduct that could constitute a criminal offense, give rise to civil liability or otherwise violate any applicable local, state, provincial, national, or international law or regulation, or encourage the use of controlled substances;</p></li><li> <p> Posting advertising or solicitation in categories that is not appropriate, or posting the same item or service in more than one category or more than once every 7 days, or posting the same ad in multiple cities on the Site;</p><ul> <li><p>(a) Posting adult content or explicit adult material unless: (i) such material is specifically permitted in designated adult categories and permitted under applicable federal, state, and local law; and (ii) you are at least 18 years of age or older and not considered to be a minor in your state of residence;</p></li><li><p>(b) Posting, anywhere on the Site, obscene or lewd and lascivious graphics or photographs which depict genitalia or actual or simulated sexual acts, as determined in the sole discretion of plannetads.com;</p></li></ul> </li></ol>',NULL,'2016-02-15 15:18:12','page',1),(202,'en_US',0,'FAQ','faq','<div class=\"uk-accordion faq\" data-uk-accordion=\"{collapse: false}\"><div class=\"accordion-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"uk-accordion-title uk-text-small\"><div class=\"\" data-uk-toggle=\"{target:\'.uk-icon1\'}\"><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-down\"></i><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-right uk-hidden\"></i> How to create a good ad? </div></h3><div class=\"uk-accordion-content uk-margin-left\"> A good Ad attracts buyers for you. It is crisp &amp; complete!\r\n\r\n		Ads lacking details may lead to unwanted calls/chats or get no response at all.\r\n\r\n		Place such an advertisement where users would like to respond without emotional content and vulgarity.\r\n\r\n		Clear Title: Explain the item or service offered in 70 characters or less.\r\n\r\n		Appropriate category: Choose a suitable category for the item or service you are offering. System, will change it automatically if found not appropriate.\r\n\r\n		Correct Price: Research the price first! It should correspond to the market pricing and reflect the actual product condition. You can also check plannetads for similar items.\r\n\r\n		Detailed description: This is the story of your items or service. Provide all relevant details:-\r\n\r\n		How long has it been used? What condition is it in?\r\n\r\n		Are there any additional accessories included?\r\n\r\n		What areas do you offer services in?\r\n\r\n		The condition, make and design, quality, purchase date, missing pieces, color, ownership and similar details can be added here.\r\n\r\n		Usually, about 2-3 sentences of quality information will be enough.\r\n\r\n		Clear Photos: Ads with photos significantly attract users. Atleast, include 2 pictures with clear images &amp; not containing links to other sites.</div></div><div class=\"accordion-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"uk-accordion-title uk-text-small\"><div class=\"\" data-uk-toggle=\"{target:\'.uk-icon1\'}\"><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-down\"></i><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-right uk-hidden\"></i> Tips for buyers and sellers</div></h3><div class=\"uk-accordion-content uk-margin-left\">  Some good practices which allow for effective and safe use of plannetads\r\n\r\nSeller\r\n\r\n    Add good quality photos and accurately describe the item you are selling.\r\n    Price your item attractively. You are likely to get more people interested in your item and service with a fair price.\r\n    Be polite in your dealings with interested buyers.\r\n    Never ask for advance payments. Buyers like to see the actual item &amp; then pay.\r\n    Always meet in person - you earn the trust of buyers.\r\n\r\nBuyer\r\n\r\n    Use proper search and filters to find exactly what you are looking for.\r\n    Agree on exact details (price, location etc.) of the transaction with the seller, ask for additional photos if necessary.\r\n    Respect each other\'s time, be polite in your dealings and transactions.\r\n    Make transactions in person, please do not transfer money in advance.\r\n    Be alert in recognizing spam and fraud ads. Do not entertain such parties for the sake your own safety.\r\n</div></div><div class=\"accordion-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"uk-accordion-title uk-text-small\"><div class=\"\" data-uk-toggle=\"{target:\'.uk-icon1\'}\"><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-down\"></i><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-right uk-hidden\"></i> Report an Ad</div></h3><div class=\"uk-accordion-content uk-margin-left\">Reporting an erroneous ad is very easy!\r\n\r\nInside of each ad, you will find the option to report that ad below the seller\'s details. You can find this option at the end of each ad.\r\n\r\nA pop pup will show, once you click on \"Report\", with the following options. To report the ad, please select the reason of the report and send.\r\n\r\nAction will be taken against these ads.</div></div><div class=\"accordion-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"uk-accordion-title uk-text-small\"><div class=\"\" data-uk-toggle=\"{target:\'.uk-icon1\'}\"><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-down\"></i><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-right uk-hidden\"></i> I cannot access \"My Account\" section</div></h3><div class=\"uk-accordion-content uk-margin-left\">This could be because the account was either suspended or blocked due to a breach of rules and/or terms of use.\r\n\r\nIn case, the above reason doesn’t hold true please follow the steps below to access your account:\r\n\r\nGo to the plannedads homepage\r\n\r\nClick on Forgot Password\r\n\r\nClick on change password link on the activation e-mail\r\n\r\nChange the Password\r\n\r\nYou should be now able to access \"My Account\". In case you are still facing problem accessing your account, please contact us and we will be more than happy to assist you.</div></div><div class=\"accordion-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"uk-accordion-title uk-text-small\"><div class=\"\" data-uk-toggle=\"{target:\'.uk-icon1\'}\"><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-down\"></i><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-right uk-hidden\"></i> How to delete my Ad?</div></h3><div class=\"uk-accordion-content uk-margin-left\">My Account option (Only Registered users):-\r\n\r\nLog in to \"My Account\" on plannetads.\r\n\r\nGo to the \"My ads\" under the user dashboard.\r\n\r\nSelect the ad, you want to delete and click \"Deactivate Ad\" below ad title. Such ads become \'Inactive\'.</div></div><div class=\"accordion-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"uk-accordion-title uk-text-small\"><div class=\"\" data-uk-toggle=\"{target:\'.uk-icon1\'}\"><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-down\"></i><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-right uk-hidden\"></i> I forgot my account password</div></h3><div class=\"uk-accordion-content uk-margin-left\">Forgot password required to log-in to Plannetads? Follow the instructions below to reset your password: -\r\n\r\nStep 1 - Fill Forgot password form. You can also reset your password while attempting to log-in by clicking on the \'Forgot Password?\' link just below \'Log in\' button.\r\n\r\nStep 2 - Receive email with a link.\r\n\r\nStep 3 - Click on the link to activate the new password.\r\n\r\nYour password with the registered email has been reset.</div></div><div class=\"accordion-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"uk-accordion-title uk-text-small\"><div class=\"\" data-uk-toggle=\"{target:\'.uk-icon1\'}\"><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-down\"></i><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-right uk-hidden\"></i> How to edit my contact information?</div></h3><div class=\"uk-accordion-content uk-margin-left\">Simple! Follow the steps given below:\r\n\r\n    Login to My Account on Plannetads\r\n    Click the Settings tab\r\n    Click \'Change contact details\' to change name or password\r\n    Finally save it.\r\n</div></div><div class=\"accordion-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"uk-accordion-title uk-text-small\"><div class=\"\" data-uk-toggle=\"{target:\'.uk-icon1\'}\"><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-down\"></i><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-right uk-hidden\"></i> How do I find an Ad for a specific item or service on plannetads?</div></h3><div class=\"uk-accordion-content uk-margin-left\">1. Keyword Search\r\n\r\nTo find an Ad for a specific item or service on plannetads, you need to enter the relevant / exact keyword and the search feature on the site will display results matching your search terms.\r\n\r\nUsers can enter keywords in the Keyword search text box as shown below.\r\n\r\n2. Search by Category/Sub category Or city wise\r\n\r\nYou can even search for items within a specific category or City. All you need to do is select the relevant category or City that matches your search term from the drop down option besides the search box.\r\n\r\nWe have also introduced an autocomplete feature to facilitate easy search.</div></div><div class=\"accordion-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"uk-accordion-title uk-text-small\"><div class=\"\" data-uk-toggle=\"{target:\'.uk-icon1\'}\"><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-down\"></i><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-right uk-hidden\"></i> How to create a good ad?</div></h3><div class=\"uk-accordion-content uk-margin-left\">A good Ad attracts buyers for you. It is crisp &amp; complete!</div></div><div class=\"accordion-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"uk-accordion-title uk-text-small\"><div class=\"\" data-uk-toggle=\"{target:\'.uk-icon1\'}\"><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-down\"></i><i class=\"uk-icon1 uk-icon-caret-right uk-hidden\"></i> Safety Tips</div></h3><div class=\"uk-accordion-content uk-margin-left\">Here are several safety guidelines to help make sure that your usage of plannetads is safe.\r\n\r\nWhile community members who use plannetads have success with buying, selling, renting or connecting with others. It is important we help keep our community members safe from people attempting to scam or defraud them. We have found that one of the best ways to address this problem is to ensure that all transactions take place locally and in-person.\r\n\r\nWe request you to take the following precautions:\r\n\r\n- When buying or selling, you should meet in-person to see the product. Learn as much as you can about who you are meeting or trading with before you complete the transaction.\r\n\r\n- Never send or wire money to sellers or buyers. This includes never mailing a cheque or using wire payment  services to pay for items found on plannetads.\r\n\r\n- Be wary of Users with no reliable contact information, who respond slowly or not at all\r\n\r\n- plannetads does not offer any sort of buyer protection. Any emails or websites that talk about such systems are scams, even if they have the plannetads logo. If you receive any emails promoting these services, please forward the message to us.\r\n\r\n- Never provide your personal or banking information (e.g. credit card number) to others over the Internet. Never give out your plannetads password, even if asked to do so in an email supposedly sent by plannetads.\r\n\r\n- Protect personal information, e.g. do not share your home address unless you know the other person and want them to visit you.\r\n\r\n- Know the site Terms of Use and Prohibited Item Policy\r\n\r\n- Make yourself aware of common scams and fraud. Do not believe the promise of large sums of money for your help in any task.\r\n\r\n- Inform plannetads of any attempted fraud or suspicious emails, Ads, or other activity by community members. In case of fraud, report it to the local authorities and inform us.\r\n\r\n- Use common sense. If something sounds too good to be true, it probably is not.</div></div></div>          ',NULL,'2016-03-04 05:10:59','page',1),(203,'en_US',0,'Help','help','<p><strong>Registration and Sign-in</strong></p><p>How do I register on Plannetads?</p><p>Registering on plannetads is now a very simple process. It takes only 1 minutes to register and post your Ads</p><p>Step 1</p><p>Click “Sign up” icon.</p><p>Step 2</p><p>Please enter the following correctly</p><p>- Name</p><p>- Valid Email Address</p><p>- Password</p><p>Please enter your valid mail address to</p><p>- Get Id &amp; Password in mailbox</p><p>- Post Ads</p><p>- Get replies to Ads</p><p>- Get alerts and special offers</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/1.png\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You will receive a confirmation email to complete your registration. Do check&nbsp;your&nbsp;SPAM e-mail to ensure&nbsp;you receive it.</p><p>Do I need to register to post Ads?</p><p>Yes, you need to be a registered user to Post Ad on the site.</p><p>What are the benefits of registering on plannetads?</p><p>Registration allows to you to</p><p>- Post free ads and Premium ads</p><p>- Get your own User ID</p><p>- Edit, delete, repost and check replies to your Ads</p><p>What is My plannetads?</p><p>\"My plannetads\" is your personal user account where you can</p><p>- View and manage your Ads</p><p>- Modify/ edit/ delete your Ads</p><p>- Check replies to your Ads</p><p>- Repost your Ads after they expire</p><p>- Update your plannetads profile</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/2.png\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Post An Ad:</strong></p><p>Why should I Sign In on plannetads?</p><p>Sign in allows you to access your account and your Ads posted on the site.</p><p>Step 1</p><p>Click the “Sign-In” link on the top right corner of the site.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/3.png\"></p><p>Step 2</p><p>&nbsp;If you have a plannetads account, enter your registered email address and password to sign into your account.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/4.png\"></p><p>How do I create / change my password?</p><p>To ensure the security of your password, password should be in length above 5 characters. Please don’t use your birthday or simple numbers like 123456 or abcdef as password. Please change your password after a certain period. You can change your password in</p><p>My plannetads -&gt; Settings -&gt; Change Password.</p><p>I have forgot my password. How do I get a new one?</p><p>You can reclaim your password if you have forgotten it.</p><p>Step1</p><p>Click “Forgot your password?” link and it will display a page to “Create a new Password”.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/5.png\"></p><p>Step 2</p><p>Fill in your registration email address to get the password, and click the “Reset my password” button.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/6.png\"></p><p>Step 3</p><p>Success message is displayed for sending the email.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/7.png\"></p><p>Step 4</p><p>In the email you receive, click on the “Change Password” link to set your new password. After which, you can sign in and change your password in “plannetads”.</p><p>What if I try to register with an email address that is already registered on plannetads?</p><p>You cannot register twice on the site with the same email address.</p><p>Also the email id and username once registered cannot be changed.</p><p>&nbsp;How do I Post Ads?</p><p>Posting an ad on plannetads is very easy and takes not more than 30 seconds. Simply follow the steps below to understand the Post Ad flow better.</p><p>Step 1</p><p>Click on the \"Post an Ad\" link in the header on all plannetads pages.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/8.png\"></p><p>Step 2</p><p>Select a categories to post</p><p>Choose the right category as given below to match the product or service you wish to sell or promote. For eg. If you are selling a car, then you should post your Ad in the category Vehicles and Sub category cars.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/9.png\"></p><p>Step 3</p><p>In this step user can fill the ad details by providing the Title, Description, Selling price, Location etc. For E.g. We have attached the screenshot for your reference. After the information, user need to save the details.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/10.png\"></p><p>Step 4</p><p>Here user can preview their ad. Please view the below screenshot.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/11.jpg\"></p><p>Step 5</p><p>In this step user can make the ad into premium and it is optional.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/12.jpg\"></p><p>Step 6</p><p>Click the \"Submit\" button to post an ad.</p><p>Is it mandatory to enter the mobile number while posting an Ad?</p><p>No, mentioning your mobile number is not mandatory. However by entering a valid mobile number you are eligible to receive SMS alerts for your Ad replies. These alerts help you respond faster to potential buyers.</p><p>What are SMS Alerts?</p><p>SMS alerts helps notify the Seller/ Poster of an Ad as soon as he gets a reply. An alert is sent to the Mobile number which you have entered at the time of Posting an Ad / Registration. You will receive SMS alerts for your Ads posted and replies received.</p><p>How much does it cost to post an Ad on plannetads?</p><p>Plannetads is a free and premium ads service. Ad cost is based on service selected by the user and also service category also vary.</p><p>How can I post a Good Ad on plannetads and get better responses?</p><p>To increase the chance of getting a good response, follow these simple tips</p><p>Title - A good title will attract more visitors to your Ad Mention important keywords in title.</p><p>Description - To get people interested, follow these simple tips</p><p>- Make the description as detailed as possible</p><p>- Make it easy for buyers to pick up the item by mentioning the location of the item and when you would be available</p><p>- Add contact information</p><p>Upload Images and video - Include up to 12 pictures to enhance your Ad. The size of all 12 photos together should not exceed 4MB and the formats are jpg,Gif and png.Video maximum length is 30 sec or 2MB.</p><p>Use these tips and other innovative ideas to make your Ad more attractive and increase your chances of getting replies. In addition you can also subscribe to plannetads \"Premium Ad\".</p><p>How do I know if someone is interested or has replied to my Ad?</p><p>- Those interested in your Ad can use the option of \"Contact seller\" on the View Ad page. Fill in the required details like email, name, and message with their contact details and you would receive an email. After you receive the email message, you can choose to respond and give additional information like phone number.</p><p>- Users also have the option to contact you on phone .You can give your contact details only if you wish to do so in the ad description area of the post ad flow. If you put your phone number, the interested parties can directly contact you.</p><p>Search and Browse</p><p>How do I find an Ad for a specific item or service on plannetads?</p><p>1. Keyword Search</p><p>To find an Ad for a specific item or service on plannetads, you need to enter the relevant / exact keyword and the search feature on the site will display results matching your search terms.</p><p>Users can enter keywords in the Keyword search text box as shown below.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/13.png\"></p><p>How do I reply to an Ad on plannetads?</p><p>You can contact posters by replying to their Ads. Fill in the required details like email, name, and message with your contact details (if you want them to contact you) to the advertiser and click on \"Submit\" button. Your reply will be sent to the poster by email.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/14.png\"></p><p>How can I report an Ad that I feel is inappropriate?</p><p>On the view Ad page, you can report Ads which you feel are fraudulent or inappropriate for site.</p><p>1. Go to the \"Report\" section on the right side of the view Ad page.</p><p>2. Choose a reporting reason from the pre-defined listed options.</p><p>3. Then click the submit icon.</p><p>5. The plannetads team will action upon the Ad within 24 hrs based on the site policies.</p><p><img src=\"http://projects.esconite.com/plannetads_dev/assets/help_images/15.png\"></p>\r\n',NULL,'2016-03-04 05:05:04','page',1),(204,'en_US',0,'Thanks Page','thanks','<p>Thanks Page Content Here <br></p>',NULL,'2016-03-03 06:55:39','page',1),(205,'en_US',0,'Conatct','contact-us','<h5 class=\"uk-text-bold\">Physical Address:</h5><p>All Correspondence<br>Plannetads<br>95 Maswell Park Road,<br>London,<br>TW3 2DP,<br>United Kingdom.</p><h5 class=\"uk-text-bold\">Email Addresses:</h5><dl class=\"uk-description-list-line\"><dt>Copyrights violation related issues</dt><dd><a href=\"mailto:abuse@plannetads.com\">abuse@plannetads.com</a></dd></dl><dl class=\"uk-description-list-line\"><dt>All help and support related issues</dt><dd><a href=\"mailto:support@plannetads.com\">support@plannetads.com</a></dd></dl><dl class=\"uk-description-list-line\"><dt>All inquiries</dt><dd><a href=\"mailto:info@plannetads.com\">info@plannetads.com</a></dd></dl>',NULL,'2016-03-28 11:40:37','page',1),(206,'fr_FR',0,'About Us','about-us','Description',NULL,'2016-03-31 05:36:00','page',1);

